'''Tamaɣuzt''' deg [[Tasnallunt|tesnallunt]] d afimidi n iferdisen i d-yettgin kra n [[tafekka tagnnawt|tfekka tagennawt]] iẓẓayen ɣef [[Ahidṛujin|uhidṛujin]] d [[hilium|uhilium]]. Imusnawen ssemrasen tanfalit n tmaɣuzt i weglam n tilin n iferdisen niden s umata acku amur ameqqran seg yitran i d-issiliɣen tanga yettwaẓren deg [[Asedday|usedday]] tegber seg [[ahidṛujin|uhidṛujin]] d [[ahilium|uhilium]]. S wanecta, [[asignew]] igebren seg [[Uksijin|weksujin]] d [[Neon|Niyun]] d [[Akaṛbun|ukaṛbun]] d [[aẓut|unitrujin]] yezmer ad yettwaglem d akken-it '''yeččur d tamaɣuzt''' seg tama [[takrura|takrurant]] ɣas akken iferdisen-nni ur ttwameggzen ara d [[amɣuz|imɣuzen]], akken daɣen ur yessefk ara ad yili urway gar n '''tmaɣuzt''' d '''imɣuzen''' d '''waqqan amaɣaz''' acku ulac aqqan akruran neɣ amaɣaz deg yitran (anagar deg yitran isemmaṭen yeṭṭafaren [[asesmel atraw|asesmel]] '''K''' yakked '''M''') yerna aqqan akruran inessen deg [[tagnit|tegnit]] ur d-izzag ara deg tegnatin n wul n yitran.<br/>
S tmusni n tmaɣuzt n kra n [[tafekka tagnnawt|tfekkiwin]] tezmer ad tili tukza n waddar-is. Acku ass mi i d-innulfa usedday (s unect n teẓri n [[Big Bang]]) yella deg tazwara igber seg uhidṛujin, yerna s tarrayt n tseddast deg uṭerṭeq ameqran yennulfa-d deg-s azal meqqren n uhilium d kra n [[Alitium|ulitium]] d [[Abriliu|ubriliu]] maca send n uṭerṭeq ameqran ''Big Bang'' ur d-lfin ara iferdisen iẓẓayen ugar-nsen. s wanecta, tamaɣuzt n yitran imezrayen tettili s ddaw n yitran itraren (i d-ilfan d imaynuten) am [[tafukt|tfukt]]

